{"tid":962403,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"【物理】古代波斯人喺沙漠都造到冰塊？（新手整片，求改善建議）","createTime":"2018-12-30T22:15:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-01T16:57:21.000Z","uid":145472,"like":403,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":69,"replies":[{"pid":"cd7d3aaa54922d0cee9fea1ed9638a10afb9ca87","tid":962403,"uid":145472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T22:15:10.000Z","msg":"大家好，我叫<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">意識橋 Ezekiel</span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n近一年，小弟去咗非洲肯亞工作。<br />\n返工唔再需要 OT，放工有時間，所以揾啲嘢搞下，整下片 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n拍知識型短片，係我一路想做嘅嘢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：<br />\n可以有藉口學下啲新奇知識，順便同各行各業各學科嘅人分享。<br />\n希望可以同觀眾交流下，大家都學得更多。<br />\n呢個亦係我頻道嘅口號「<strong>異花傳粉，以知識維新</strong>」嘅意思。<br />\n--------------<br />\n片:<br />\n沙漠中無電都可以造冰？古代波斯人「神奇造冰術」(上集)<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/-y6T9GvXUK0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F-y6T9GvXUK0&d=4gXlBYZ6EL0HpDvDIV0rjDCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=26317b7b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/-y6T9GvXUK0</a><br />\n<br />\n公元前的古代雪櫃和雪糕！古代波斯人「神奇造冰術」(下集)<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/h_lqeeYqsZw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fh_lqeeYqsZw&d=4gXlBYZ6EL0HpDvDIV0rjDCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=09f5f56d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/h_lqeeYqsZw</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n《暗淡藍點》[粵語]：為全人類帶來希望和反思的訊息<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/N5PASPhchWU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FN5PASPhchWU&d=4gXlBYZ6EL0HpDvDIV0rjDCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=40a8b666\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/N5PASPhchWU</a><br />\n<br />\n--------------<br />\n暫時仲係新手，剪片剪得好慢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n遲下熟手啲，有埋製作流程，希望做到一星期一片（希望2019年內做到）。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n求狠批，<br />\n指點下小弟，點樣整會好睇啲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":