re":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T21:00:11.000Z","msg":"見到咁長真係嚇親<br />\n用緊兩倍速都聽到樓主講緊咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0899f40420669d47f4feabefc64ff10d9e3ec33","tid":962403,"uid":145472,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T21:05:59.000Z","msg":"樓主喺非洲肯亞同大家講聲Happy New Year <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 呢邊遲香港五個鐘，啱啱新年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n去咗陣隔離屋吹個水啫，<br />\n多咗咁多巴絲留言，<br />\n多謝晒各位肯花時間睇同俾意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我一定逐個細心睇，以後整好睇啲。<br />\n<br />\n暫時睇似乎語速太慢係最大問題，<br />\n明白，我之後講快啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我追一追返個 post 先"},{"pid":"28ec51f5fcfcccaf3b3de4b6d70b6c4ff60bda8e","tid":962403,"uid":38648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T21:14:28.000Z","msg":"內容OK嘅, 不過語速同停頓位太過份<br />\n我係用兩倍速播放, 正常過原版, 其實依然聽得明你講乜"},{"pid":"dae09e8659cbf415f34f1ac5e52d316910ac755c","tid":962403,"uid":168430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T21:15:53.000Z","msg":"未得閑睇<br />\n不過正皮支持先"},{"pid":"8d253cf8074756a4f06a3d3d4c428dc5fa20c843","tid":962403,"uid":145472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5ebc31e1823f3547399c48154dac80c5408b4565","tid":962403,"uid":55533,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T05:56:55.000Z","msg":"見到你個名就諗起motherfucker<br />\nThe path of the righteous man is beset on all sides by the Inequities of the selfish and the tyranny of evil men <br />\nBlessed is he who, in the name of charity and good will, shepherds the weak through the valley of darkness for he is truly his brother's keeper and the finder of lost children <br />\nAnd I will strike down upon thee with great vengeance and furious Anger those who attempt to poison and destroy my brothers <br />\nAnd you will know, my name is the Lord when I lay my vengeance upon thee"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T21:41:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我都好鐘意嗰一幕，勁型"},{"pid":"12df611cd69cd12713529ddbdc66ee600fd7fb6e","tid":962403,"uid":145472,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"844c849951359c16245ba7349d994e43bf9b1bc7","tid":962403,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T17:20:53.000Z","msg":"唔好意思搭單問下，肯亞做野危唔危險？飲食如何？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T21:50:07.000Z","msg":"（離題答你）<br />\n<br />\n唔太危險嘅，我住首都。<br />\n較危險係啲偏遠少少地區，有部落之間嘅衡突，我唔會去到嗰啲地方。<br />\n我工作地方有情報機制，有咩危險會SMS 通知所有員工。<br />\n<br />\n例如前排，市中心搞馬拉松，<br />\n有情報話可能有恐怖襲擊，叫我地嗰幾日唔好去市中心。<br />\n不過好彩無事發生。<br />\n<br />\n上年肯亞總統大選有好大爭議，好多示威，不過我當時未黎到做嘢。<br />\n<br />\n疾病方面，我打晒針去。<br />\n係要注意防蚊驚瘧疾。<br />\n<br />\n飲食其實 OK啱我胃口，<br />\n無咩難食嘢嘅。"},{"pid":"dac56f7af2009d4b8195cfd2942fd9634da34998","tid":962403,"uid":145472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"de17038e267e98c347876565e45acba59f643ba1","tid":962403,"uid":2679,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T18:44:57.000Z","msg":"樓主你用翻本身個速度<br />\n之後自己較1.25/1.5咁 先擺上黎 <br />\n唔岩試到岩 咪解決到問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T21:52:39.000Z","msg":"真心極度感謝你呢個建議，<br />\n你個名真係叫好人<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我聽朝瞓醒就試一試work 唔 work 。"},{"pid":"031c33a30f72df4d7ce33dd5480e5eaf6d0790c2","tid":962403,"uid":127716,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0628b4db8ac28b737501f2985cafdc7f9ce83f98","tid":962403,"uid":145472,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"quote":{"pid":"cc8f30e6f7a687f4f8b9831cd2a14bb2ad763690","tid":962403,"uid":78429,"like":76,"dislike":1,"score":75,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T23:40:13.000Z","msg":"唔好意思，把聲唔好聽有冇得改善<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外個storytelling style好悶，好似照書讀咁<br />\n建議參考下大台例如PBS 或者Vox啲人點講嘢<br />\n<br />\nThumbnail design就慢慢學啦，太clickbait會似啲無聊channel"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T04:15:44.000Z","msg":"多謝巴打咁認真俾comment <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n1）我試下好聽啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n2）明白，我平時都有睇呢啲YouTube channel，原來自己落手做都唔係咁易，我會認真學下佢地。<br />\n3）thumbnail  真心未識搞，引人注意同 clickbait 之間點拿捏 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T22:09:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/UZHGEyCYgTc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FUZHGEyCYgTc&d=4gXlBYZ6EL0HpDvDIV0rjDCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=b811957e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/UZHGEyCYgTc</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n學下人地適當時候放下音樂<br />\n有時搞下笑<br />\n<br />\n不過唔岩你性格就咪格硬做"},{"pid":"5bed87f4b8b35db432fa7d810fdd1fafb6bfe4e1","tid":962403,"uid":29278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T22:19:22.000Z","msg":"留"},{"pid":"c30f7b9daa048cdd341dbf3aed5590a261fbb3ce","tid":962403,"uid":135762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T22:22:14.000Z","msg":"支持 已訂閱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86ee5af74d89ba0d566d4f15c97c39e697b090f2","tid":962403,"uid":134747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T23:09:19.000Z","msg":"加下背景音樂會好啲 加油 做得好好<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"292ec63b8b4e42c196ae7672187564f4c5156b86","tid":962403,"uid":36290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T23:11:11.000Z","msg":"啲topic 都得意，會有興趣繼續啲<br />\n加油"},{"pid":"089e46058c6be9a067aa271691426011d254fba0","tid":962403,"u